       </span>
      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d278n1-ptr" id="PJA09d278n1">1</a>
      
   <p>For <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s activities while at Bordeaux between 29 Jan. and 2 Feb., see <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-02-02-0010-0001-0018" class="document">2:433</a>; <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary of John Quincy Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. David Grayson Allen, Robert J. Taylor, and others, Cambridge, 1981. ]">JQA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-03-01-02-0002-0001-0023" class="document">1:32</a>.</p>

